webpackJsonp([0x7e945d184c8e],{7907:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{post:{html:'<p>The Shopblogger Bj√∂rn Harste is <a href="http://www.shopblogger.de/blog/archives/5203-24-Stunden-geoeffnet.html">taking advantage</a> of the extended shopping hours in Bremen and is now opening his Spar supermarket 24 hours from Monday through Saturday. He <a href="http://www.shopblogger.de/blog/archives/5205-14-Kunden.html">blogged</a> <a href="http://www.shopblogger.de/blog/archives/5208-gaehn.html">through</a> the <a href="http://www.shopblogger.de/blog/archives/5214-Bilanz-der-ersten-Nachtoeffnung.html">night</a> his "first night out".</p>\n<p>Of course for restaurants 24 hour opening is nothing new or special. We are already open until 3 am (4 am on weekends). We\'re considering going 24 hours ourselves (at least in the Drive-Thru), not so much for the sales as for daily maintenance and security. There\'s always something to clean.</p>',fields:{title:"24/7",date:"18 Jun 2007",url:"https://papascott.de/2007-06-18-247/"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/2007-06-18-247/",prev:{fields:{title:"Fun Fun Fun",date:"17 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-17-fun-fun-fun/"}},next:{fields:{title:"Censr at Flickr",date:"20 Jun 2007",slug:"/2007-06-20-censr-at-flickr/"}}}}}});
